name: Good Times - S.F.R.  TOUR COVER
description:
Good Times - Shorter . Faster. Radder. Tour Cover...

"...stop by south end, POVERTY..heading for the cove.."


...If you're a fan of Good Times you know that we like to write songs about the beach where we're from. There were 90 records set aside for tour covers..we decided to take sand from 3 spots mentioned in no shirt no shoes (the cove, poverty, davies lake) and make special covers to take elsewhere when we're on the road..The cove covers were made in Feb.'12 and sold out..These were left over POVERTY covers from our weekend with Rock Bottom Dec. '12. Each one is hand made, stamped out of 30, stamped labels with the dates and a picture of sunrise at Poverty Beach, Cape May.

***ATNN EUROPE AND PLACES OTHER THAN NORTH/SOUTH AMERICA...PLEASE ORDER TWO (2) ITEMS...THANKS!!!***
